{"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"DBusConnectionRef","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"title":"DBusConnectionRef","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"DBusConnectionRef"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO17DBusConnectionRefV","symbolKind":"struct","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Structure"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusConnection"},{"type":"text","text":" type is used for D-Bus connections to remote"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"peers such as a message buses."}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/dbusconnectionref"]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/init(_:)-3d0r8","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/init(_:)-4zzsy","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/init(_:)-522j3","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/init(_:)-76sh","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/init(_:)-dj5z","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/init(addressFinish:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/init(addressSync:flags:observer:cancellable:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/init(cPointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/init(constPointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/init(finish:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/init(gconstpointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/init(gpointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/init(mutating:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/init(opaquePointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/init(sync:guid:flags:observer:cancellable:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/ptr"],"generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"anchor":"Type-Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/new(finish:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/new(sync:guid:flags:observer:cancellable:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/newFor(addressFinish:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/newFor(addressSync:flags:observer:cancellable:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/unowned(_:)"],"generated":true,"title":"Type Methods"},{"anchor":"Default-Implementations","generated":true,"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/AsyncInitableProtocol-Implementations","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/DBusConnectionProtocol-Implementations","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/GWeakCapturing-Implementations","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/InitableProtocol-Implementations","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef\/ObjectProtocol-Implementations"]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/AsyncInitableProtocol","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionProtocol","doc:\/\/GIO\/4GLib14PointerWrapperP","doc:\/\/GIO\/10GLibObject14GWeakCapturingP","doc:\/\/GIO\/10GLibObject0B8ProtocolP","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/InitableProtocol"],"kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"DBusConnectionRef","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is a low-level API that offers a lot of flexibility. For instance,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"it lets you establish a connection over any transport that can by represented","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as a [class"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/IOStream"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This class is rarely used directly in D-Bus clients. If you are writing","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"a D-Bus client, it is often easier to use the [func","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.bus_own_name","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"],"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[func","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.bus_watch_name"},{"text":"] or [func","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.DBusProxy.new_for_bus"},{"text":"] APIs.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"As an exception to the usual GLib rule that a particular object must not"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"be used by two threads at the same time, "},{"code":"GDBusConnection","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"s methods may be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"called from any thread. This is so that [func"},{"code":"Gio.bus_get","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"] and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[func"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.bus_get_sync"},{"type":"text","text":"] can safely return the same "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusConnection"},{"text":" when","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"called from any thread.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Most of the ways to obtain a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusConnection"},{"type":"text","text":" automatically initialize it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"(i.e. connect to D-Bus): for instance, [func","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.DBusConnection.new","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"] and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[func","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.bus_get"},{"type":"text","text":"], and the synchronous versions of those methods, give you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"an initialized connection. Language bindings for GIO should use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[func","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.Initable.new","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"] or [func","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.AsyncInitable.new_async"},{"text":"], which also","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"initialize the connection.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you construct an uninitialized ","type":"text"},{"code":"GDBusConnection","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", such as via"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[ctor"},{"code":"GObject.Object.new","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"], you must initialize it via [method","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.Initable.init"},{"text":"] or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.AsyncInitable.init_async"},{"type":"text","text":"] before using its methods or properties."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Calling methods or accessing properties on a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusConnection"},{"type":"text","text":" that has not"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"completed initialization successfully is considered to be invalid, and leads","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to undefined behaviour. In particular, if initialization fails with a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"GError","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the only valid thing you can do with that "},{"code":"GDBusConnection","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is to","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"free it with [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GObject.Object.unref"},{"text":"].","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","text":"An example D-Bus server","anchor":"An-example-D-Bus-server","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Here is an example for a D-Bus server:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/gitlab.gnome.org\/GNOME\/glib\/-\/blob\/HEAD\/gio\/tests\/gdbus-example-server.c","type":"reference","isActive":true}]},{"anchor":"An-example-for-exporting-a-subtree","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"An example for exporting a subtree"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Here is an example for exporting a subtree:","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/gitlab.gnome.org\/GNOME\/glib\/-\/blob\/HEAD\/gio\/tests\/gdbus-example-subtree.c"}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"An example for file descriptor passing","anchor":"An-example-for-file-descriptor-passing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Here is an example for passing UNIX file descriptors:"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/gitlab.gnome.org\/GNOME\/glib\/-\/blob\/HEAD\/gio\/tests\/gdbus-example-unix-fd-client.c","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]},{"text":"An example for exporting a GObject","type":"heading","anchor":"An-example-for-exporting-a-GObject","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Here is an example for exporting a [Object](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/object","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/gitlab.gnome.org\/GNOME\/glib\/-\/blob\/HEAD\/gio\/tests\/gdbus-example-export.c","type":"reference","isActive":true}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentatio